---
description: CLI and TUI display standards
globs:
  - "src/agent/cli.c"
  - "src/agent/tui.c"
---

- Include `seaclaw/design_tokens.h` for all display constants
- Colors: `SC_COLOR_ACCENT`, `SC_COLOR_SUCCESS`, `SC_COLOR_ERROR`, `SC_COLOR_WARNING`, `SC_COLOR_INFO`, `SC_COLOR_MUTED` — never hardcode `\033[...m` ANSI sequences
- Box drawing: `SC_BOX_VERT`, `SC_BOX_HORIZ`, `SC_BOX_TL`, `SC_BOX_TR`, `SC_BOX_BL`, `SC_BOX_BR` — never hardcode UTF-8 byte sequences
- Symbols: `SC_CHEVRON` for prompt, `SC_CHECK` for success, `SC_CROSS` for failure
- Reset: always use `SC_COLOR_RESET` after colored output
- Bold/dim: `SC_COLOR_BOLD`, `SC_COLOR_DIM`
